[[[description]]]
This macro checks to see if the given zval is a constant. See the [`IS_TYPE_CONSTANT`](http://phpinternals.net/docs/is_type_constant) macro for further information on constant types in the Zend Engine.

This macro also has a counterpart macro, `Z_CONSTANT_P`, that accepts a pointer to a `zval` instead.

